          <h6>Online billing and payment</h6>
          <p>All billing and payment for student fees 
            and campus charges is online only. Find out <a href="http://www.berkeley.edu/calparents/letterhome/2005/spring/studentservices.html">how 
            the system works</a> or <a href="http://billingservices.vcbf.berkeley.edu/StudentServices/eBillInfo.htm">learn 
